<br>
I'm Leeni, a lvl 52 Mage on the Cazic Thule Server. I personally made a mage because the person that introduced me to EQ is a mage. I had no idea what I was doing. lol EQ is my first online game ever. Well, at lvl 52 in 4 mos..I'd say I've done pretty well. lol I love playing Leeni. I have started a barage of other chars from a druid, wizzy, cleric, monk, chanter...just about every class. I always come back to Leeni. Not only are we the Walmart of Norrath, but our nukes and pets are unsurpassed. It saddens me when grouped with players that don't realize what an assest a mage is to a group. We bring our own tank..what more could group members want? hehee  Well, that's my two cents worth. I love being a mage..got lucky that my first char choice was the right one for me!<br>
